    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i just sit here in the quiet and think about how much i'm taking up. my knees are failing, i can't even make a cup of tea without feeling like i'm in the way... i see my kids' faces when they visit and i can just see the exhaustion in them. i hate being the reason they're stressed. everything just feels like so much work for everyone else now.",
